    "description": "<p none=\"\" open=\"\" outline:=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\">Anel Redondo Personalizado Prata com Banho de Ouro</span></span></p>\n\n<p none=\"\" open=\"\" outline:=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 78, 78); font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249);\">Esse modelo &eacute; com&nbsp;at&eacute; 8 caracteres (nome no cora&ccedil;&atilde;o), a frase escolhida ir&aacute; depender do tamanho do aro, se for tamanho pequeno n&atilde;o comporta uma frase muito longa</span></p>\n\n<p none=\"\" open=\"\" outline:=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\">Medida: 9mm</span></span></p>\n\n<p none=\"\" open=\"\" outline:=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\">Espessura: 2mm&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n\n<p none=\"\" open=\"\" outline:=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \">Celebre momentos e sentimentos com o <strong data-end=\"381\" data-start=\"320\">Anel Redondo Personalizado em Prata com Banho de Ouro 18k</strong>. Com design minimalista e toque sofisticado, essa joia exclusiva permite gravar nomes, datas ou palavras especiais, tornando-se uma pe&ccedil;a cheia de significado.</p>\n\n<p none=\"\" open=\"\" outline:=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p none=\"\" open=\"\" outline:=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none !important; font-weight: 700;\">PRAZO DE CONFEC&Ccedil;&Atilde;O DE 25 DIAS &Uacute;TEIS</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p none=\"\" open=\"\" outline:=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p none=\"\" open=\"\" outline:=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \">&#10004;&#65039; <strong data-end=\"573\" data-start=\"545\">Personaliza&ccedil;&atilde;o Exclusiva</strong> &ndash; Grave o que for importante para voc&ecirc;: nomes, datas, iniciais ou palavras marcantes.<br data-end=\"662\" data-start=\"659\" />\n&#10004;&#65039; <strong data-end=\"687\" data-start=\"665\">Acabamento Premium</strong> &ndash; Feito em <strong data-end=\"721\" data-start=\"699\">prata 925 leg&iacute;tima</strong> com banho de ouro 18k, unindo resist&ecirc;ncia e brilho duradouro.<br data-end=\"786\" data-start=\"783\" />\n&#10004;&#65039; <strong data-end=\"819\" data-start=\"789\">Design Redondo Minimalista</strong> &ndash; Vers&aacute;til e elegante, combina com todos os estilos e ocasi&otilde;es.<br data-end=\"886\" data-start=\"883\" />\n&#10004;&#65039; <strong data-end=\"923\" data-start=\"889\">Presente Afetivo e Sofisticado</strong> &ndash; Ideal para eternizar la&ccedil;os em datas especiais como anivers&aacute;rios, Dia dos Namorados, Dia das M&atilde;es e muito mais.<br data-end=\"1039\" data-start=\"1036\" />\n&#10004;&#65039; <strong data-end=\"1076\" data-start=\"1042\">Joia Atemporal e Significativa</strong> &ndash; Mais do que um acess&oacute;rio: uma lembran&ccedil;a personalizada para carregar sempre.</p>\n\n<p none=\"\" open=\"\" outline:=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\">Todas as nossas pe&ccedil;as acompanham:</span></span></p>\n\n<p none=\"\" open=\"\" outline:=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\">-&gt; Certificado de garantia de 1 ano nas pe&ccedil;as&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n\n<p none=\"\" open=\"\" outline:=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\">&nbsp;-&gt; </span></span></p>\n\n<div none=\"\" open=\"\" outline:=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \">\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none !important; margin: 0px 0px 15px; line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\">-&gt; Temos uma equipe preparada para te auxiliar no p&oacute;s venda</span></span></p>\n</div>",
